Introducing Undetectable ChatGPT Chrome (UCG) Extension by SmartStudi.com

A new convenient way to use ChatGPT in an undetectable way. This extension communicates with ChatGPT behind the scenes and lets you send questions without having a tab open or having a visible chat on screen.

To use Undetectable ChatGPT (UCG) Chrome Extension you will need to sign up for a free account at SmartStudi.com
